─────────────────────────────────────────
  GLITCH_OS  //  v4.0
─────────────────────────────────────────

SETUP
─────
  pip install pygame
  python glitch_os.py


FOLDER STRUCTURE
─────────────────────────────────────────
  glitch_os.py
  log/
      page_1.txt     ← one dialogue page per file
      page_2.txt
  music/
      song.wav       ← .wav  .ogg  .mp3  .flac
  images/
      photo.png      ← .png  .jpg  .jpeg  .bmp  .gif


APPS
─────────────────────────────────────────
  LOG        → dialogue/story reader with typewriter effect
  MUSIC      → audio player with visualiser and track list
  CALC       → calculator (keyboard + mouse, type any expression)
  IMGS       → image viewer (zoom with scroll, pan with drag)


CONTROLS
─────────────────────────────────────────
Desktop
  Double-click icon      → open app
  ESC                    → quit

All windows
  Drag title bar         → move
  Drag bottom/right edge → resize
  _ button (title bar)   → minimize to taskbar
  X button               → close
  Taskbar button         → toggle show/hide (lit = open, dim = hidden)

LOG
  NEXT / LAST            → navigate pages (typewriter)

MUSIC
  Click track row        → play  (click again = pause/resume)
  PREV / NEXT            → skip
  LOOP                   → loop current track  (LOOP* = active)
  Progress bar           → click or drag to scrub

CALC
  Click buttons          → input
  Keyboard               → type expressions directly
  Enter                  → evaluate
  Backspace              → delete last char
  ESC (while focused)    → clear

IMGS
  PREV / NEXT            → browse images
  Scroll wheel           → zoom in/out
  Click + drag           → pan when zoomed


WINDOW ANIMATION
─────────────────────────────────────────
Windows "unroll" downward when opening and
collapse back up when closing — the height
shrinks to 0 smoothly so nothing pops.

─────────────────────────────────────────